{"tid":1758250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際戰線幫幫手】外國朋友想收集大家嘅抗爭歌","createTime":"2019-11-27T02:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T02:44:51.000Z","uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb128a73db62b066e3a0e3f392900ad38b88d77","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:40:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">是咁的，有外國朋友想整一個網頁，每個月以一個抗爭地方做主題整 playlist，<span style=\"color: red;\">收集同記錄世界各地唔同抗爭者喺社運時期聽嘅歌，原因喺想以音樂 connect 大家 ，以唔同方法保留大家抗爭時嘅感覺同埋經歷</span>，同時分享世界唔同角落嘅抗爭消息。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港會係第一個 playlist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>，之後會繼續收集嚟自智利，伊拉克，加泰隆尼亞等等地方嘅歌。遲少少可能會開一個 physical location 喺法國 Normandy 一個叫做 Caen 嘅城市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想要咩歌：<br />\n可以係代表到運動嘅歌曲 / 自家製 / 任何喺運動期間觸動到自己嘅音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n樓主就幫大家寫咗《榮光》先，大家自由發揮，鐘意嘅都可以分享下聽歌感受，或者點解揀呢啲歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者大家有咩 creative input 都可以發表下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n朋友 message 原文：<br />\n<br />\nThe &laquo; Cobbles of Caen &raquo; / Le pav&eacute; Caennais<br />\n<br />\nI am writing you about a French project I&rsquo;m involved in, a local news website which aims to inform the public about local struggle actions. I&rsquo;m undertaking the &laquo; cultural page &raquo;. The project has just started and the website is still under-construction. The idea is to publish, every month a music playlist made by a collective in struggle, a good way to bring people to it. As the Yellow Jacket in France is now finding new ways to mobilize people, we need to adapt and share our struggles. <br />\n<br />\nHK is engaged in a fight against CPC since several months, we support you and would like to inform others about your cause. Behind the singularities of national actions, music is keen to gather people.<br />\n<br />\nThe playlist we are working on is wildly open and I would like to integrate songs of the HK protest. So what do you listen to recently ? It can be a protest song, HK pop or even mainstream music.<br />\n<br />\nThanks for your attention. And don&rsquo;t give up the fight !<br />\n<br />\nAll the best!"},{"pid":"de11f7b818517a033ea612b921d97448bf53d254","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb456ab9c518debef127fefff3fe49838df0ca1d","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cdbea417e85e48a7d9848bae090a9b7220ce22","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:42:01.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21346caf69090d6daf593a3a5eb2b376735469ac","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:42:12.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba672cdd23a8c1c600951eea851dda1066c2a63","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"幫幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3d260300a4cc0035ff6da9bc2b15c4b1ca2412","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:43:18.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b081c20a6f8b437c9e82f2de4bd8d8829241d9","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7988d90a1bad2934ff912e54f9e6c52925f4f8af","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:44:20.000Z","msg":"咩歌都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6583449512b1c8bea86f4b7cffc5460018a560","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b082a45b516c1f4608c7a659ec11413247db9f22","tid":1758250,"uid":299887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:44:51.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}